alright, no router = no no-ip
try using hamachi, no lagg
www.hamachi.cc
download the free version
click the triangle, create network
network name: your scape name
network pass: the pass people will enter, dont make it anything personal
post your hamachi info, port, and ip + some pics would help on server adv. thread
click runserver.bat
your good to go
